entry.title: reisxd/TizenBrew
entry.summary:
A way to experience modded websites and you can install newer apps without fighting with Tizen Studio

TizenBrew


Thank you @Zyborg777 for the logo!

TizenBrew is a way to experience modded websites (like TizenTube) and you can install newer apps without having to deal with Tizen Studio multiple times.
